OL,3,CWoman guilty of manslaughter of ex-
OL,4,Cpartner who died weeks after acid
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FA woman has been found guilty of the
OL,8,Fmanslaughter of her former partner who
OL,9,Fdied after an acid attack in Plymouth.
OL,11,FDanny Cahalane was targeted in the
OL,12,Fattack in February last year, and died
OL,13,Fin hospital ten weeks later.
OL,15,FHis 35-year-old ex-partner and mother
OL,16,Fof his child, Paris Wilson, was found
OL,17,Fguilty of manslaughter but cleared of
OL,18,Fhis murder.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
