OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1778782268
OL,3,CWoman guilty of manslaughter of ex-
OL,4,Cpartner who died weeks after acid
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FA trial, involving ten defendants, has
OL,8,Fbeen running since January at
OL,9,FWinchester Crown Court.
OL,11,FThe court heard Mr Cahalane was a drug
OL,12,Fdealer and owed a 'large amount' of
OL,13,Fmoney to another drug dealer, known as
OL,14,F'Frost'.
OL,16,FOn Thursday, the jury returned its
OL,17,Fverdicts.
